<font size="12.000000pt" face="Helvetica"><span style="font-size: 12.000000pt; font-family: Helvetica">zanych z odst</span></font><font size="12.000000pt" face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 12.000000pt; font-family: Arial">a&#808;</span></font><font size="12.000000pt" face="Helvetica"><span style="font-size: 12.000000pt; font-family: Helvetica">pieniem od umowy. Niemniej jednak, w Rekomendacji wskazano, </span></font><font size="12.000000pt" face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 12.000000pt; font-family: Arial">z&#775;</span></font><font size="12.000000pt" face="Helvetica"><span style="font-size: 12.000000pt; font-family: Helvetica">e rezygnacja z ochrony mo</span></font><font size="12.000000pt" face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 12.000000pt; font-family: Arial">z&#775;</span></font><font size="12.000000pt" face="Helvetica"><span style="font-size: 12.000000pt; font-family: Helvetica">e poci</span></font><font size="12.000000pt" face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 12.000000pt; font-family: Arial">a&#808;</span></font><font size="12.000000pt" face="Helvetica"><span style="font-size: 12.000000pt; font-family: Helvetica">gn</span></font><font size="12.000000pt" face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 12.000000pt; font-family: Arial">a&#808;c&#769; </span></font><font size="12.000000pt" face="Helvetica"><span style="font-size: 12.000000pt; font-family: Helvetica">za sob</span></font><font size="12.000000pt" face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 12.000000pt; font-family: Arial">a&#808; </span></font><font size="12.000000pt" face="Helvetica"><span style="font-size: 12.000000pt; font-family: Helvetica">np. obowi</span></font><font size="12.000000pt" face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 12.000000pt; font-family: Arial">a&#808;</span></font><font size="12.000000pt" face="Helvetica"><span style="font-size: 12.000000pt; font-family: Helvetica">zek dostarczenia przez klienta innego zabezpieczenia, zmian</span></font><font size="12.000000pt" face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 1