<node CREATED="1428878451434" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_574517089" MODIFIED="1447377429296" TEXT=" The impact of the worldwide turmoil on the financial risk management">
<node CREATED="1428878461065" ID="ID_1652773082" MODIFIED="1428878461748" TEXT="The main problem since the emergence of the crisis in the Polish market has been the rapidly drying liquidity on the interbank market."/>
<node CREATED="1428878240222" ID="ID_1266036320" MODIFIED="1428878240937" TEXT="Due to the crisis in the interbank market, both in Poland and internationally, the Bank decided to fund long-term CHF assets with direct credit lines within the Group, and thus gained independence of funding from the expensive and illiquid interbank market of fx swaps and CIRS."/>
</node>
