      <div class="layoutArea">
        <div class="column">
          <p>
            <font size="3" face="Helvetica">Ze wzgl</font><font size="3" face="TT1AAo00">e&#x328;</font><font size="3" face="Helvetica">du na brak zabezpiecze</font><font size="3" face="TT1AAo00">n&#x301; </font><font size="3" face="Helvetica">przed ryzykiem kursowym u kliento&#x301;w indywidualnych Komisja Nadzoru Bankowego wprowadzi&#x142;a &#x201e;Rekomendacj</font><font size="3" face="TT1AAo00">e&#x328; </font><font size="3" face="Helvetica">S dotycz</font><font size="3" face="TT1AAo00">a&#x328;</font><font size="3" face="Helvetica">c</font><font size="3" face="TT1AAo00">a&#x328; </font><font size="3" face="Helvetica">dobrych praktyk w zakresie ekspozycji kredytowych zabezpieczonych hipotecznie&#x201d;. Okre</font><font size="3" face="TT1AAo00">s&#x301;</font><font size="3" face="Helvetica">la ona sposo&#x301;b wyliczania zdolno</font><font size="3" face="TT1AAo00">s&#x301;</font><font size="3" face="Helvetica">ci kredytowej w takich przypadkach &#x2013; dla kliento&#x301;w, zaci</font><font size="3" face="TT1AAo00">a&#x328;</font><font size="3" face="Helvetica">gaj</font><font size="3" face="TT1AAo00">a&#x328;</font><font size="3" face="Helvetica">cych kredyt hipoteczny w walutach, banki b</font><font size="3" face="TT1AAo00">e&#x328;</font><font size="3" face="Helvetica">d</font><font size="3" face="TT1AAo00">a&#x328; </font><font size="3" face="Helvetica">j</font><font size="3" face="TT1AAo00">a&#x328; </font><font size="3" face="Helvetica">wylicza</font><font size="3" face="TT1AAo00">c&#x301; </font><font size="3" face="Helvetica">w z&#x142;otych, a potrzebn</font><font size="3" face="TT1AAo00">a&#x328; </font><font size="3" face="Helvetica">do oblicze</font><font size="3" face="TT1AAo00">n&#x301; </font><font size="3" face="Helvetica">kwot</font><font size="3" face="TT1AAo00">e&#x328; </font><font size="3" face="Helvetica">kredytu podwy</font><font size="3" face="TT1AAo00">z&#x307;</font><font size="3" face="Helvetica">sz</font><font size="3" face="TT1AAo00">a&#x328; </font><font size="3" face="Helvetica">o 20%.<b>&#xa0;Przepis ten wchodzi w </b></font><b><font size="3" face="TT1AAo00">z&#x307;</font><font size="3" face="Helvetica">ycie 1 kwietnia 2006 roku, przy czym banki b</font><font size="3" face="TT1AAo00">e&#x328;</font><font size="3" face="Helvetica">d</font><font size="3" face="TT1AAo00">a&#x328; </font><font size="3" face="Helvetica">mia&#x142;y trzy miesi</font><font size="3" face="TT1AAo00">a&#x328;</font><font size="3" face="Helvetica">ce na jego wdro</font><font size="3" face="TT1AAo00">z&#x307;</font><font size="3" face="Helvetica">enie. </font></b>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
