pe">one przez ca</span><span style="font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: PalatinoLinotype">&#x142;</span><span style="font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: PalatinoLinotype">y okres kredytowania. Dalsze przeliczanie dokonywane jest &#x2013; w odniesieniu do poszczego&#x301;lnych rat kredytu &#x2013; z waluty obcej na z</span><span style="font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: PalatinoLinotype">&#x142;</span><span style="font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: PalatinoLinotype">oto&#x301;wki. Z tego wzgl</span><span style="font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: PalatinoLinotype">e&#x328;</span><span style="font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: PalatinoLinotype">du takie kredyty sp</span><span style="font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: PalatinoLinotype">&#x142;</span><span style="font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: PalatinoLinotype">acane s</span><span style="font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: PalatinoLinotype">a&#x328; </span><span style="font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: PalatinoLinotype">przewa</span><span style="font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: PalatinoLinotype">z&#x307;</span><span style="font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: PalatinoLinotype">nie w z</span><span style="font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: PalatinoLinotype">&#x142;</span><span style="font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: PalatinoLinotype">oto&#x301;wkach. </span></font>
