<node CREATED="1428619667340" ID="ID_1592648557" MODIFIED="1428619671776" TEXT="In financial markets, comparative advantage exists when the same risk is priced differently in different markets. If borrowing costs differ across markets, then issuers can reduce their overall financing costs by raising funds in the market in which each has a comparative cost advantage and swapping the proceeds. ">
